INTRODUCTION
------------

The OUM Cookiehub module provides easy cookiehub integration in your website.
This module implements the cookiehub integration code and provides a field
plugin for adding the cookiehub cookie declaration to any entity type.

REQUIREMENTS
------------

This module requires no modules outside of Drupal core.

INSTALLATION
------------

 * Install as you would normally install a contributed Drupal module. Visit
   https://www.drupal.org/node/1897420 for further information.

CONFIGURATION
-------------

 * Configure the cookiehub in Administration » Configuration » Webservices » Cookiehub:

   - Enter the urls (production and development) for the cookiehub integration code

   - Enable / Disable development mode based on your environment

 * To enable the cookie declaration on an entity type, manage the entities' fields, and add the 'Cookiehub cookie declaration' field.

